b0714754-192a-4529-9948-5bc5f6c2183a.2cb39e4c-8e4b-404a-b098-2d0124022e6f.description=Check the current date and time, and returns a java DateAndTime formatted string of it. Responses\: success - Date/time retrieved successfully. failure - Date/time could not be retrieved. b0714754-192a-4529-9948-5bc5f6c2183a.3e2b5161-8192-4772-9ce7-4584ad6e8f9e.prompt=HostName\: b0714754-192a-4529-9948-5bc5f6c2183a.42f15503-4d12-48cf-a800-84af9cc015a0.prompt=Alternate Credentials - Password\: b0714754-192a-4529-9948-5bc5f6c2183a.60f0134c-fa50-43a8-85c5-88c765966e12.description=
Searches for a specific property in LDAP.  Returns the first result, stores the rest in a collection that is accessable via the LDAPSearchNextResult operation.

Input Parameters\:
Host - name or IP address of LDAP server to query
DN - base DN for search
Filter - search filter (ex. member\=CN\=User1,CN\=Users,DC\=mydomain,DC\=local)
PropertyName - name of property to return (ex. distinguishedName)
User - name of user to connect to LDAP as
Password - password of user

Responses\:
Ojbect(s) Retrieved - was able to retrieve objects from LDAP.  First value is returned as returnResult result
No Objects Found - either no objects where found or an error occurred.  See returnResult for more information

See returnResult for more information b0714754-192a-4529-9948-5bc5f6c2183a.93dd4364-ddab-4f70-a877-0da66fd6bacc.prompt=Alternate Credentials - UserName\: b0714754-192a-4529-9948-5bc5f6c2183a.96ecebe0-b95c-4485-af5a-a5090c5851bf.prompt=Domain Controller Name\: b0714754-192a-4529-9948-5bc5f6c2183a.971cdad6-2881-4a83-b4f1-c100c8211a02.prompt=Alternate Credentials - UserName\: b0714754-192a-4529-9948-5bc5f6c2183a.af148429-4cec-4498-9674-16214dad4a53.prompt=Mailbox User\: b0714754-192a-4529-9948-5bc5f6c2183a.b71fdb1a-3fe0-4034-872f-f9a1f8c4dbee.description=
Converts an string date time to an Active Directory Time Stamp (Integer8)

Input Parameters\:
adTimeStamp - string representation of the time stamp returned by ad

Responses\:
Passed - converted successfully (value is op result)
Failed - failed to convert
b0714754-192a-4529-9948-5bc5f6c2183a.d6627cc1-c006-47bb-b351-fd156d488547.prompt=Alternate Credentials - Password\: b0714754-192a-4529-9948-5bc5f6c2183a.description=
Checks to see if an account is locked.

Inputs\:
    host - The host to check for events on
    altuser - The username to use when authenticating with the host
    altpass - The password for altuser
    mbuser - The name of the user whose mailbox is checked

Responses\:
    success - The operation completed as stated in the description
    failure - The operation completed unsuccessfully
b0714754-192a-4529-9948-5bc5f6c2183a.e4c7e876-c59c-4e07-8935-62f70ac6af95.description=
Executes an Expression (e.x value1 \=\= value2)

Input Parameters\:
value1 - the value to threshold with
value2 - the threshold to threshold against
operator - (\=\=, \!\=,  >, >\=, <, <\=) the type of threshold
okstring - string to push into returnResult if the threshold has not been passed
failedstring - string to push into the returnResult if the threshold has been passed

Responses\:
True - the expression is true
Fales - the expression is false
